## Troubleshooting

### Check Service Status
```bash
docker-compose ps
```

### View Logs
```bash
docker-compose logs -f <service-name>
```

### Reset Everything
```bash
docker-compose down -v
docker-compose up -d --build
```

## Default Credentials

All default credentials are documented in the main README.md file.

